pullrequest.title: Enable urdf2gazebo to parse multiple collision/visual elements per link

content.raw: If `createCollision` is a class member function, it should be capitalized and invocation of the function should start with `this->`. It looks like all the function calls in this file are incorrect. They all need to be capitalized and all the invocations need a `this->`.
